r($,"aN0","py",()=>{var q="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.iconic.socialv&hl=en"
return A.a([A.m_("Handyman Service",'Presenting "Handyman Service App" - Handyman Service is a user-friendly, on-demand app built with Flutter, designed to connect users with reliable home service professionals quickly and seamlessly. Featuring a range of services, from plumbing and electrical work to cleaning and repairs, the app offers real-time booking, secure payments, and integrated ChatGPT support for instant, AI-powered assistance.',"","https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.iqonic.servicebooking","https://apps.apple.com/in/app/handyman-service-user/id1591427211"),A.m_("SocialV","SocialV is a dynamic social networking app, seamlessly connected with a BuddyPress (WordPress) backend, designed to create an engaging and interactive community experience. It offers a rich set of features including customizable activity feeds, an integrated shop module for e-commerce, forums for discussions, a courses module for educational content, and a GamiPress module to gamify user engagement. Users can also form and join groups, fostering community connections and participation, making SocialV the ultimate platform for building and managing vibrant online communities.","",q,q),A.m_("Pawlly","Pawlly is an all-in-one pet care app designed to make pet parenting easier and more enjoyable. With a focus on health, wellness, and convenience, Pawlly connects pet owners to a range of essential services, from veterinary consultations and health tracking to grooming and pet supplies. The app features a dedicated pet health tracker to monitor vaccinations, diet, and wellness appointments, ensuring pets stay healthy and happy. Pawlly\u2019s integrated pet shop offers a wide selection of premium food, toys, accessories, and grooming products, all tailored to meet the unique needs of your pet. Whether you're managing daily care, scheduling check-ups, or shopping for pet essentials, Pawlly is your trusted companion in providing the best for your furry friend. ","","https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pawlly.customer&hl=en","https://apps.apple.com/in/app/pawlly/id6458044939"),A.m_("Streamit","Streamit is a powerful and flexible streaming app built with Flutter, designed to deliver seamless access to movies, TV shows, and video content. Integrated with a WordPress backend, Streamit enables easy content management and customization for administrators, while offering users a smooth and engaging viewing experience. With features like personalized recommendations, watch lists, and high-quality streaming, Streamit is the ideal platform for creating and managing a content-rich streaming service on mobile.","","https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.iqonic.streamit&hl=en",""),A.m_("Vizion AI","Vizion AI is an innovative app designed to empower creators with advanced AI tools, built with Flutter and integrated with ChatGPT-4o and ChatGPT -4o mini. This app enables users to generate content effortlessly, from writing and brainstorming to generating images and video scripts. ","","https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.iqonic.vizionai&hl=en","https://apps.apple.com/in/app/vizion-ai/id6478587159"),A.m_("Nabit App","Explore, engage, and enjoy with our location-based community app designed for event enthusiasts. ","","https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nabit.app&hl=en","https://apps.apple.com/us/app/nabit-app/id6670331526"),A.m_("Instancy","Transform your learning experience with the Instancy App, the ultimate mobile learning platform that puts knowledge at your fingertips. Designed for learners and professionals, Instancy Lite brings powerful tools and interactive content straight to your device, ensuring you stay ahead in today\u2019s fast-paced world.","","https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.instancy.instancy_lite&hl=en_IN&pli=1","https://apps.apple.com/in/app/instancy/id1287604826"),A.m_("Enterprise Learning","Streamline employee training and enhance workforce performance with the Enterprise Learning App\u2014your all-in-one solution for corporate learning and development. Designed for organizations of all sizes, this app empowers employees to access, engage with, and excel in their learning journeys anytime, anywhere.","","https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.instancy.enterpriseapp","https://apps.apple.com/in/app/enterprise-learning/id1566857527"),A.m_("Ai Skill Hub","This app serves as a comprehensive gateway to a vast universe of AI-powered tools and applications. It's designed to streamline daily tasks and boost productivity by offering a centralized hub for various AI solutions.","","https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.aiTools.app","https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ai-skill-hub/id6740995605")],A.a1("u<Iq>"))})
